This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for interpreting noun compounds. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of crowdsourcing and data collection, which could fall under cs.LG (Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves the construction of a dataset, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with the semantics of noun compounds, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
